00:17:23,810 --> 00:17:24,480
Apa?!

316
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:28,350
Ya, semuanya berjalan sesuai rencana, Jii...

317
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:30,490
Mereka jatuh ke dalam sepenuhnya,

318
00:17:30,820 --> 00:17:34,860
