Bonsoir, Kaito Kid.

323
00:17:52,940 --> 00:17:53,840
Chat Noir?!

324
00:17:54,340 --> 00:17:56,650
Jika kau masih di sana,

325
00:17:57,180 --> 00:18:00,420
