00:24:05,270 --> 00:24:08,040
Pintu di peron 3 akan ditutup.

414
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:11,710
Harap berhati-hati
terhadap pencuri yang masuk ke dalam kereta.

415
00:24:12,120 --> 00:24:13,380
Cuma bercanda!

416
00:24:13,380 --> 00:24:14,180
Minggu depan,

417
00:24:14,180 --> 00:24:17,420
